description:
DJ James Kennedy from Bravo's Vanderpump Rules stops by to talk about the show, music, & SO much more. Danny also recaps #RHONY, Southern Charm, Drag Race, & Mariah's People mag cover. PLUS, Ashley Bell (Director/Star of Love & Bananas) pops by.
